      "ingredient_lines": [],
      "instruction": "Step 3"
    },
    {
      "ingredient_lines": [],
      "instruction": "Brown Rice Variation: Use 1 cup long-grain brown rice and 1 3/4 cups broth. In Step 2, simmer for 45 minutes. Remove the rice from the heat and let stand, covered, for 15 minutes before adding the vegetables."
